text: Dmytro Semeniv (; born 24 June 1998) is a professional Ukrainian football midfielder who plays for Hirnyk-Sport Horishni Plavni. ==Career== Born in Odesa Oblast, Semeniv is a product of the FC Viktoriya from the settlement Avanhard in the Odesa Oblast and FC Chornomorets youth sportive schools. He played for Real Pharma Odesa in the Ukrainian Second League, but in February 2016 signed a contract with Chornomorets Odesa and played in the Ukrainian Premier League Reserves.
